summary: Completed comprehensive testing of bot calling application with Infobip integration. Backend APIs fully functional with 100% success rate. Frontend UI working correctly with dark glassmorphism theme, two-column layout, and real-time SSE integration. Only minor issue found with Clear Logs functionality.

ui_bugs.issue: Clear Logs button doesn't fully clear all log entries (1 entry remains after clearing)

passed_tests: Backend API root endpoint (/api/) returns status
Backend API POST /api/calls/initiate creates call and returns call_id
Backend API GET /api/calls/{call_id}/events SSE endpoint streams events
Frontend loads with two-column layout (Bot Logs | Call Setup)
Call Configuration form has all required fields
Message Scripts section with all textareas functional
Call Steps tabs work correctly and are clickable
Start Call button initiates call and shows real-time logs
Hang Up button appears when call is active and terminates call
Call button transforms from cyan glow (Start) to red glow (Hang Up)
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix Clear Logs button functionality to properly clear all log entries when clicked
